System wrapper for pl and ps for arria10soc board.

Parameters
FPGA_TECHNOLOGY
parameter

Type of FPGA, such as Ultrascale, Arria 10. 103 is for Arria 10.

FPGA_FAMILY
parameter

Sub type of fpga, such as GX, SX, etc. 1 is for SX

SPEED_GRADE
parameter

Number that corresponds to the ships recommeneded speed. 2 is for 2.

DEV_PACKAGE
parameter

Specify a number that is equal to the manufactures package. 3 is for FBGA.

DELAY_REFCLK_FREQUENCY
parameter

Reference clock frequency used for ad_data_in instances

ADC_INIT_DELAY
parameter

Initial Delay for the ADC

DAC_INIT_DELAY
parameter

Initial Delay for the DAC
